  <h2 style="text-align:center">Recycling of E-waste and the Li-batteries</h2>
  <p class="hin">
    Hello amigos!.Today we observed that lot of plastic waste is dumped into the publi places.
    It may leads to the lot of pollution.
  Recycling of these wastes is very useful to save the nature. 
  </p>
  <p> 
    <img src="recycle.jpg" style="padding-right:2em;">
    <img src="recycle2.jpg" style="padding-right:2em;">
    <img src="recycle3.jpg" style="padding-right:2em;"><br>
    <p>
      Steps to follow in collecting the plastic waste and the li-batteries.<br>
       Collect the wastages from the public places like sea shore,road sides and other places.<br>
       Be careful while collecting the Li-batteries. They are made with some poisonous chemicals.<br>
  </p>
  <p style="font-size: larger;font-family: italic;background-color: light green;color:rgb(233, 225, 233)">
    <b>Creating awareness in People</b><br>
    Conduct some  meetings to create the hazards happening to the people by using the large amount of plastic.
    It causes lot of health problems.
    Using of Li-batteries leads to the Global warming.
    Those are very sensitive to temperature.
    If the battery is completely discharged then it longer to be recharged again.
    It is realtively expensive.
    If the separator gets damaged. It can burst into flames.
  </p>
  <p>
    Advantages of the collecting the E-waste and the Li-batteries.
    It reduces pollution.
    It Saves the Earth from the Global Warming.
  </p>

